From kasperdanielhansen at gmail.com  Mon Sep 29 04:49:28 2014
From: kasperdanielhansen at gmail.com (Kasper Daniel Hansen)
Date: Sun, 28 Sep 2014 22:49:28 -0400
Subject: [Bioc-devel] GenomicFiles: some random issues
